datamodels.description: Data of Vaccine Candidates per Phase
datamodels.sql:
SELECT CASE
           WHEN stage_of_development = 'Pre-clinical' THEN '0. Pre-clinical'
           WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase I' THEN '1. Phase I'
            WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase I/II'
    or stage_of_development =  'Phase II' THEN '2. Phase II or Combined I/II'
           WHEN stage_of_development =   'Phase III' THEN '3. Phase III'
           WHEN stage_of_development = 'Authorized' THEN '4. Authorized'
         END AS clinical_stage,
       COUNT(*) AS count
FROM covid_vaccines
GROUP BY CASE
    WHEN stage_of_development = 'Pre-clinical' THEN '0. Pre-clinical'
  WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase I' THEN '1. Phase I'
  WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase I/II'
       or stage_of_development = 'Phase II' THEN '2. Phase II or Combined I/II'
  WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase III' THEN '3. Phase III'
  WHEN stage_of_development = 'Authorized' THEN '4. Authorized'
         END
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 10000
OFFSET 0;

  WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase III' THEN '3. Phase III'

         END

LIMIT 10000
OFFSET 0;

           WHEN stage_of_development = 'Pre-clinical' THEN '0. Pre-clinical'
           WHEN stage_of_development = 'Phase I' THEN '1. Phase I'

LIMIT 10000
OFFSET 0;
